          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">πύργος</span></b> : <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">tower, turreted
            wall;</span> fig., of Ajax, <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">πύργος
            Ἀχαιῶν</span>, <i><span class="en">Il. 11.556</span></i>; his
          shield also is compared to a tower, <i><span class="en">Il.
            7.219</span></i>, <i><span class="en">Il. 11.485</span></i>; of a
          ‘column,’ ‘compact body’ of troops, <i><span class="en">Il.
            4.334</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
